name: #001 Ayrton Senna McLaren 1993
description:
Ayrton Senna (1960-1994) was a brazilian F1 driver.

He had 41 wins, 80 podiums, was pole position 65 times, and won 3 championships (1988, 1990 and 1991). 

Driving McLarens's car MP4/8, he was 2nd on the 93' Grand Prix

Ayrton Senna is a F1 legendary driver. To most he is the greatest driver of all time!
